{"word":"Jehoahaz","slug":"jehoahaz","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jehoahaz</b> - <b>(a)</b> Son of Jehu, king of Israel<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=35'>2Ki 10:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=13&verse=1'>2Ki 13:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=13&verse=9'>2Ki 13:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=1'>2Ki 14:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=8'>2Ki 14:8</a><p/><b>(b)</b> Son of Jehoram, king of Judah<p/><b>--SEE</b> Ahaziah, AHAZIAH<p/><b>(c)</b> Or Shallum, son of Josiah, king of Judah<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=30'>2Ki 23:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=34'>2Ki 23:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=1'>2Ch 36:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=22&verse=11'>Jer 22:11</a>"}]}